Class DependencyPlugin

java.lang.Object
org.bukkit.plugin.PluginBase
org.bukkit.plugin.java.JavaPlugin
com.heretere.hdl.spigot.DependencyPlugin
All Implemented Interfaces:
CommandExecutor, TabCompleter, TabExecutor, Plugin
public abstract class DependencyPlugin
extends JavaPlugin
Used to automatically load dependencies for a plugin. It extends JavaPlugin.

    • fail

      protected abstract void fail​(@NotNull @NotNull Set<@NotNull Throwable> genericErrors, @NotNull @NotNull Set<@NotNull DependencyLoadException> dependencyErrors)
      Called when the dependency engine fails to load the supplied dependencies. Supplies a set of errors that occurred during the process. You should provide a manual process to downloading the dependencies here.
      Parameters:
      genericErrors - The generic errors that occurred during the dependency loading process.
      dependencyErrors - The errors related to a specific dependency that occurred during the loading process.
